This is a perfect studio synch flash for small studio camera or digital photography. With the digital revolution well under way, a lot of people are finding that large, heavy lights are completely unneccessary to make great product photos for online sales, portraits and other purpose. There are many systems available on ebay, but none is as lightweight and economical as this system. This flash lamp besides having an internal sensor to activate flash, can be connected via a connecting cable to a camera for synchronization. The lamp is accompanied by key test, light charge. The charging time is very low. Designed with modern technologies, will help you to get professional results at each step.

The flash has a sensor built in already! This is ideal for most of the point and shoot and digital cameras that do not have a PC Sync adapter for external flash.

STUDIO STROBE SYNCH FLASH DYNASUN PRO WOF4004 LIGHTING

This is a perfect studio synch flash for small studio camera or digital photography. With the digital revolution well under way, a lot of people are finding that large, heavy lights are completely unneccessary to make great product photos for online sales, portraits and other purpose. There are many systems available on ebay, but none is as lightweight and economical as this system. This flash lamp besides having an internal sensor to activate flash, can be connected via a connecting cable to a camera for synchronization. The lamp is accompanied by key test, light charge. The charging time is very low. Designed with modern technologies, will help you to get professional results at each step.

The flash has a sensor built in already! This is ideal for most of the point and shoot and digital cameras that do not have a PC Sync adapter for external flash.

STUDIO STROBE SYNCH FLASH DYNASUN PRO WOF4004 LIGHTING

This is a perfect studio synch flash for small studio camera or digital photography. With the digital revolution well under way, a lot of people are finding that large, heavy lights are completely unneccessary to make great product photos for online sales, portraits and other purpose. There are many systems available on ebay, but none is as lightweight and economical as this system. This flash lamp besides having an internal sensor to activate flash, can be connected via a connecting cable to a camera for synchronization. The lamp is accompanied by key test, light charge. The charging time is very low. Designed with modern technologies, will help you to get professional results at each step.

The flash has a sensor built in already! This is ideal for most of the point and shoot and digital cameras that do not have a PC Sync adapter for external flash.
